{"tid":958033,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［極詭異] 大台驚現神秘廣告，網友不安","createTime":"2018-12-27T13:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T14:48:43.000Z","uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b6994c7b295b5dbd313bbc03cb0984fb347b2e08","tid":958033,"uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZwVgrAY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZwVgrAY.png&h=c10d0147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今時今日電視廣告收費愈嚟愈貴，有好多公司轉改賣網上廣告減低成本。可以喺大台聖誕期間黃金時段賣廣告嘅通常係大公司。但近日一個由「蘋果廣告公司」發出嘅廣告就引來網民不安啊！事關整段廣告無任何對白、淨係播住低清煙花，配上劉華嘅《真我的風采》。呢5秒廣告喺黃金時間播出，真係相當詭異啊。廣告一出，網民都掀起瘋狂討論，有人話可能係暗示嚟緊嘅煙花匯演會有出事，又有人話催眠緊觀眾。<br />\n<br />\n網民仲調查到2003年都曾經有個蘋果電影嘅廣告，個廣告形式一模一樣，然而當年呢個廣告播出後就爆發沙士，網民又估今次會唔會又係表示有病毒爆發。不過呢啲一切都係猜測，並無憑證嘅。最令人意外嘅係網上完全搵唔到呢間公司嘅任何資料，只能夠搵到佢有商業登記，但無公司註冊。<br />\n<br />\n睇返大台閒日黃金時段嘅廣告收費，5秒嘅廣告最貴收29萬，最平就2萬3。但呢個每節廣告時段都播，都要唔少錢。難怪網民會覺得呢個來歷不明嘅廣告咁詭異。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_645861_0&amp;i=20181227\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_645861_0%26i%3D20181227&d=wP1V4d3dEokp1rN2RNzFfwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=810563e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_645861_0%26i%3D20181227&h=e813ae54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_645861_0&amp;i=20181227</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc1c347c23965b843418dad9805b73ed22d6339","tid":958033,"uid":61463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:07:11.000Z","msg":"Lihkg&gt;公海&gt;Lihkg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c07b67febfbcbbcb5553eddd6c2ac3f44128068","tid":958033,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:38:23.000Z","msg":"有人已經查到公司地址、公司老闆<br />\n樓主E家先黎大發現WOW唔WOW D"},{"pid":"2b10af48bc0fb1ebbfdbe813875a4d7129886cc3","tid":958033,"uid":226972,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T14:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q8zEpZb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq8zEpZb.png&h=e8a0e539&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}